He was spotted by a local who raised the alarm with the electricity officials who cut off the power supply.

In total he remained at the top of 
the pylon for five hours doing his gymnastic performances and singing 
popular Chinese songs, ignoring requests from family and friends to come
down.

Only towards the end
after having stripped off his shirt and his shoes did he finally agreed
to come down when some of his creditors confirmed they would no longer 
pursue him so rigorously to get the money back.

